Usage: set_disable_timing [-help] <object_list> [-from <pin_name> -to <pin_name>]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<object_list>             # List of instance, instance pin, library cell,
                          # library cell pin objects, collection of library
                          # arcs or collection of timing arcs (string, required)
-from <pin_name>          # Specifies the source pin of the cell arc
                          # (string, optional)
-to <pin_name>            # Specifies the sink pin of the cell arc
                          # (string, optional)